  "summary": "HashiCorp Nomad’s exec2 task driver vulnerable to a symlink attack",
  "details": "HashiCorp Nomad’s exec2 task driver prior to 0.1.2 is vulnerable to arbitrary file read and write on the client host as the Nomad process user through a symlink attack. This vulnerability (CVE-2026-8052) is fixed in version 0.1.2 of the exec2 task driver.",
